I need help replenishing my balance. I added a card but can't pay. Who can help me with this issue?

I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble with your payment. I recommend contacting your bank to resolve the payment matter or adding a different payment method. If you choose to update your account with a different payment method, don't forget to resubmit your ads! Another short-term solution is to add ad credits to your account. For more details, you can refer to our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide). If you need further assistance, please let me know!
